00:13:18,260 --> 00:13:18,710
Pangeran.

227
00:13:19,380 --> 00:13:22,350
Setelah kita menyelesaikan
hal selanjutnya bersama,

228
00:13:22,590 --> 00:13:24,110
kita bisa saling jujur.

